---

This repository reverse-engineers and re-implements `UCL-PLAIN.COM`, an
intro released 1996-03-03 by **SkullCODEr / United Crackers League**.
The original binary is included as `UCL-expected.bin` (and a copy at
`web/UCL-PLAIN.COM` is fetched at runtime by the JS port). All rights
to the original 1996 work and its creative content (code, music data,
visual design, scroll-text greets) remain with SkullCODEr / UCL —
those bytes are preserved verbatim for historical / educational
purposes and are not covered by the MIT licence above. The MIT
licence applies only to the new material in this repository: the
disassembly annotations, documentation, and the JS/Canvas port.
